    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can spur your allies into action to react faster to imminent threats. For the duration of this shout, you and your allies are immune to sleep and fascinated. In addition, when first affected by this shout, any sleeping allies immediately wake up, fascinated allies automatically break free of the fascinate effect, flat-footed allies no longer count as flat-footed even if they have not acted yet, and allies lying prone may stand up as an immediate action, provoking attacks of opportunity as normal.</p>\n",
